column5: So how was it today Papa Smurf(As Marc would say)did you get some Walleyes or Muskie.  We are waiting  MTP
Yeah! A real report with a detailed description of the days events, and multiple pictures!... and keep it clean!!!
I just want to see the fish porn!!! So come on and show us fish skin
So Roy how was the fishing on the Larry?               MTP

If yanno somebody's goin fishin' and you don't hear back from them about it, it usually means the fish weren't bitin'.   You live real close to the "Larry" Mike, how about you givin' it a fish and tell us how it was?
